{"tid":380784,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]  點樣擺脱無腦煩膠","createTime":"2017-08-30T11:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T12:50:59.000Z","uid":137178,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4bb788e8a77f6c24c5b55c7c0ef322a5f68f6d6a","tid":380784,"uid":137178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:36:05.000Z","msg":"我去迎新日<br />\n 入個hall聽佢介紹迎新之類<br />\n坐我旁邊有個肥仔潦我傾計 <br />\n我答左佢一句 點知係惡夢既開始<br />\n成程煩膠住我 我初頭以為佢係d鐘意傾計既人<br />\n就無點理 <br />\n慢慢聽得出佢係d憨鳩無腦既人<br />\n成程認屎認屁 以為自己聰明 搞笑<br />\n我開始唔理佢但無用  <br />\n轉地方又成程跟住我 <br />\n結果比佢煩足3個鐘<br />\n最後走個時先賣甩佢<br />\n<br />\n各位ching點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢好似當左我係朋友 係咁問我名 我無答佢 <br />\n我同佢讀同一科 我唔想成個學期比人破壞哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee21521cef075d1e549eebfb5bce37ab480bdbf","tid":380784,"uid":137178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcaf482e850100331d49692b2d248b78e7d110bc","tid":380784,"uid":137178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6e89ad7a9778670ca9c70a8607483676ba77a0","tid":380784,"uid":137178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:37:38.000Z","msg":"利申 男"},{"pid":"dfddb7896346eb1c0eef0c5dc5572cc27e8a306f","tid":380784,"uid":137178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:38:43.000Z","msg":"有無人救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3838a46ec8087cdccb2621959cdff7022c8d1b69","tid":380784,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:39:47.000Z","msg":"扮GAY"},{"pid":"135edf799cfcd919b7b3a2d01538cbe792c855ea","tid":380784,"uid":137178,"li